    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) is a specimen of mechanical purity. Powered by a rear-mounted 3.6L flat-six engine featuring VarioCam Plus, it delivers linear power through a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring zero cowl shake. Critically, the IMS bearing has been retrofitted with a dual-row ceramic solution, and the rear main seal is bone dry. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors for exceptional thermal management. Finished in collector-grade condition with a documented service history, this 911 represents the zenith of analog driver engagement.",
      "price": 47500.0,
