      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly stunning shape\u2014honestly, it feels just like it did the day it left the showroom. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, keeping it polished and pristine inside and out. It drives incredibly smooth and is just waiting for someone who will love it as much as I have. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
